            <div class="title">
                Hydro-Electric Development (Scotland) Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1943-04-07/debates/d0b5d4c9-8504-453d-8915-b84423b5f556/DavidBrownAndSonsHuddersfield(Directors)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
